nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE HEADING WEST-NORTHWESTWARD OVER THE CENTRAL EAST PACIFIC...
summary: ...HENRIETTE HEADING WEST-NORTHWESTWARD OVER THE CENTRAL EAST PACIFIC... As of 11:00 AM HST Tue Aug 05 the center of Henriette was located near 17.0, -125.6 with movement WNW at 16 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1003 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
